Dexter uses the autotools (./configure && make && sudo make install ) 
and depends on:
- pcre
- libxml2
- libxslt (with exslt)

Debian/Ubuntu:
------------------------------------------------------------------------
sudo apt-get install libxslt1-dev libpcre3-dev build-essential
./configure
make
sudo make install

Mac OS X with MacPorts:
------------------------------------------------------------------------
sudo port install pcre
./configure
make
sudo make install

Windows:
------------------------------------------------------------------------
I've made no attempt to be Windows-friendly, yet.  I'd love some 
contributions!

Other OS/Configurations:
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Haven't tried.